{"tid":879572,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK]Zero Hour CS1.6 喪屍伺服器 (新增8款槍械圖+追加遙控式C4)","createTime":"2018-10-28T05:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T13:52:49.000Z","uid":218395,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59ea29dcb9ca41f805c283eb22e02afa67680dc3","tid":879572,"uid":218395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"IP:112.119.92.7:27015<br />\n<br />\n開放時間<br />\n星期1-6:晚上7:pm-00:00am<br />\n星期日:下午2:00PM-00:00am<br />\n<br />\n使用Zombie Plague 4.3 (大多數機率發生單人傳染模式)<br />\n<br />\n以下是少機率發生其他模式<br />\n刺客模式<br />\n多重傳染<br />\n瘟疫模式<br />\n狙擊模式<br />\n刺客模式<br />\n大決戰模式<br />\n<br />\n由於剛開服，預計玩家人數0人，希望有興趣玩的玩家耐心等待。<br />\n<br />\n喪屍蟲介紹取代一般喪屍炸彈，可發放5隻小蟲追蹤人類將其感染。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Dh9ogq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Dh9ogq.jpg&h=029228cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雷射劍介紹自認曾經在刀仔server，有超強刀法的你，這個將會成為你生存到最後一刻的武器，任何喪屍被斬也會死掉。究竟你出劍快，還是喪屍出手快?因為只要被喪屍抓到一下，你就會被感染了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uH1YPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uH1YPS.jpg&h=f7cd938e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n餘下7款槍械圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4kbBBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4kbBBE.jpg&h=2140c1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7SQR90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7SQR90.jpg&h=13c062a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzrFuWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzrFuWF.jpg&h=be270f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOjosJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOjosJm.jpg&h=971f58bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNdD03r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNdD03r.jpg&h=742ed6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img sr